<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١ - <span class="c1">"الجرح والتعديل"</span> <span class="c2">(٦/ ٣٠٥)</span> وفيه عن أبي حاتم: <span class="c1">"شيخ"</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٢ - <span class="c1">"الثقات"</span> لابن حِبَّان <span class="c2">(٧/ ٢٤٢)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٣ - <span class="c1">"التقريب"</span> <span class="c2">(٢/ ٨٥)</span> وقال: <span class="c1">"شيخ، من السابعة"</span>/ تمييز.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
